title: Kerala PSC Recruitment 2025 - Apply Online for Pharmacist Posts
description: Kerala Public Service Commission has declared the official notification for 2025. To fill up the vacancies for Pharmacist Jobs. Those candidates who have qualified in the 10th Pass can grab this chance and apply for the Kerala PSC Recruitment 2025 . Here we include the age limit, selection process, salary structure, education details, application fee, and how to apply for these posts. Interested candidates can apply online before the last date of application. If you are looking for more, here...
